TO FIX: Update your MCP config to include the headers field:

{
  "mcpServers": {
    "synter-ads": {
      "url": "https://mcp.syntermedia.ai",
      "headers": {
        "X-Synter-Key": "syn_your_key_here"
      }
    }
  }
}

1. Get your API key at https://syntermedia.ai/developer
2. Add the headers block above to your MCP config
3. Restart the MCP connection (/mcp)", "developer_portal": "https://syntermedia.ai/developer", "fix": {"config_key": "headers", "config_value": {"X-Synter-Key": "syn_your_key_here"}, "config_path_hint": "mcpServers.synter-ads.headers"}}
